		<p class="lead index-lead">
			The GUI is a front-end development framework designed for multi-brand, accessible, responsive, mobile first projects. It provides HTML, CSS, LESS and
			JavaScript to describe how all of the core interface elements should look and behave. The GUI can also be used as a point of reference for UX and UI
